Meet <b>Miley</b>, our Citizen of the Week!<br><br>She lives on a little street in Golden Valley known as Twilight Lane. This math whiz has tons of energy and a glowing smile. Since June 6, 2006, she has dazzled Millsberry with her soccer skills and razor sharp smarts.<br><br>Miley has been playing soccer for many years, and is extremely agile on her feet. She has quick reflexes and great endurance. As a team captain, she cheers on her teammates and keeps everyone in the right mindset&mdash;to win! Her coaches over the years have always commented on Miley's positive attitude and her wish to keep growing as a player.<br><br>When it comes to decorating her house, Miley finds the Sylvie sofas to be the most comfortable sofas around. The <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=3">Furniture Store</a> has some offerings she likes, but nothing's more relaxing than sinking into the cushions of one of her many Sylvie sofas. Check out how many she has!<br><br>Stop by <a href='/home/?user=alyssafuji96'>36403-A Twilight Lane</a> to meet this cool girl. Thanks for being a good citizen, Miley, and congratulations on being named Citizen of the Week!</div>
